  • Constructor Details

    • WeatherData

      public WeatherData(String weatherMain, String weatherDescription, String weatherIcon, double temperature, double feelsLike, double minTemperature, double maxTemperature, double windSpeed, int windDirection, double rainAmount)
      Constructor creates a new WeatherData object.
      Parameters:
      weatherMain - Main weather phenomenon ("Rain", "Snow")
      weatherDescription - Description of the weather
      weatherIcon - Code of icon which describe the weather
      temperature - Temperature in Kelvin
      feelsLike - Feels like Temperature
      minTemperature - Minumun temperature in Kelvin
      maxTemperature - Maximun temperature in Kelvin
      windSpeed - Wind speed meters per second
      windDirection - From which direction the wind is blowing
      rainAmount - How much rain is expected to rain in one hour
